minha fé nos pais.

706
00:26:56,179 --> 00:26:58,529
Obrigado George.

707
00:26:58,573 --> 00:27:05,101
♪

708
00:27:06,625 --> 00:27:09,192
- [exala profundamente]

709
00:27:09,236 --> 00:27:15,764
♪

710
00:27:18,027 --> 00:27:19,333
Aqui vai nada.

